cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.SE, cs.NE 

This paper is about automated machine learning (AutoML) tools, specifically a modification to the Tree-Based Pipeline Optimization Tool (TPOT). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DM (Data Mining). The paper also discusses the use of evolutionary algorithms, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
